            "options": {
                "mode": "markdown",
                "content": "## Alert Taxonomy\nThis dashboard is taxonomy-driven. A JSON API datasource named **Alerts Taxonomy API** should point to the lightweight server (e.g. `python scripts/serve_taxonomy_http.py --port 8000`).\n\nEndpoint reference:\n- `/taxonomy` (full object)\n- `/taxonomy/alerts` (alerts array)\n\nRegenerate artifacts (Markdown / JSONL / HTML):\n`````\npython scripts/sync_alert_taxonomy.py --rules docker/prometheus_rules.yml --taxonomy ../../alerts_taxonomy.json --lint --emit-markdown docs/alerts_taxonomy.generated.md --emit-jsonl docs/alerts_annotations.jsonl --emit-html docs/alerts_taxonomy.html\n`````"
